\[\frac{\Delta L_r}{L_r} + (\kappa_T - 4) \frac{\Delta T}{T} + \kappa_\rho \frac{\Delta \rho}{\rho} + \frac{4}{3} \frac{\Delta \rho}{\rho} 
= 0 \ \Longrightarrow \ 
