\[\frac{\epsilon_\mathrm{n}}{L_r} \left\{ \epsilon_T \frac{\Delta T}{T} + \epsilon_\rho \frac{\Delta \rho}{\rho} + (\kappa_T - 4) \frac{\Delta T}{T} + \left( \kappa_\rho + \frac{4}{3} \right) \frac{\Delta \rho}{\rho}\right\} - \frac{sT}{L_r} \Delta S 
